## 4. 인터랙션 및 마이크로 애니메이션 정의

### 4.1 버튼 터치 상태

```css
/* 버튼 상태 애니메이션 */
@keyframes button-press {
  0% {
    transform: scale(1);
  }
  50% {
    transform: scale(0.95);
  }
  100% {
    transform: scale(1);
  }
}

.calc-button:active {
  animation: button-press 0.1s ease;
}

/* 리플 효과 */
.calc-button {
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.calc-button::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 50%;
  left: 50%;
  width: 0;
  height: 0;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  transition: width 0.3s, height 0.3s;
}

.calc-button:active::before {
  width: 200px;
  height: 200px;
}
```

### 4.2 화면 전환 애니메이션

```css
/* 화면 전환 */
@keyframes slide-in-right {
  from {
    transform: translateX(100%);
    opacity: 0;
  }
  to {
    transform: translateX(0);
    opacity: 1;
  }
}

@keyframes slide-out-left {
  from {
    transform: translateX(0);
    opacity: 1;
  }
  to {
    transform: translateX(-100%);
    opacity: 0;
  }
}

.screen-transition-enter {
  animation: slide-in-right 0.3s ease;
}

.screen-transition-exit {
  animation: slide-out-left 0.3s ease;
}

/* 페이드 전환 */
@keyframes fade-in {
  from { opacity: 0; }
  to { opacity: 1; }
}

@keyframes fade-out {
  from { opacity: 1; }
  to { opacity: 0; }
}

.fade-transition-enter {
  animation: fade-in 0.2s ease;
}

.fade-transition-exit {
  animation: fade-out 0.2s ease;
}
```

### 4.3 결과 표시 애니메이션

```css
/* 결과 계산 애니메이션 */
@keyframes result-update {
  0% {
    transform: scale(1);
    opacity: 1;
  }
  50% {
    transform: scale(1.05);
    opacity: 0.8;
  }
  100% {
    transform: scale(1);
    opacity: 1;
  }
}

.calc-display__result.updating {
  animation: result-update 0.3s ease;
}

/* 숫자 카운트업 애니메이션 */
.calc-display__result.counting {
  animation: pulse 0.5s ease-in-out;
}

@keyframes pulse {
  0%, 100% {
    transform: scale(1);
  }
  50% {
    transform: scale(1.02);
  }
}
```

### 4.4 오류 상태 표시

```css
